name: Eye Am Eye
description:
Eye Am Eye

Afraid to close my eyes.
I stare at a world 
that spins and divides

Hallucinations. 
velvet dreams,
Taunt the room inside.

Only I can see
that I am I,
beyond this heavy scene.

Every weighted blink
Fractionally
Turns into a scream. 

1/1 NFT Collection by artist Jimi Albert
